el-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cv-so-voi-so-yeu-ly-lich-su-khac-biet-chinh-de-lua-chon-giua-hai.html\/#Su_khac_biet\" title=\"S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t\">S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cv-so-voi-so-yeu-ly-lich-su-khac-biet-chinh-de-lua-chon-giua-hai.html\/#CV\" title=\"CV\">CV<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cv-so-voi-so-yeu-ly-lich-su-khac-biet-chinh-de-lua-chon-giua-hai.html\/#So_yeu_ly_lich_mau\" title=\"S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch m\u1eabu\">S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch m\u1eabu<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cv-so-voi-so-yeu-ly-lich-su-khac-biet-chinh-de-lua-chon-giua-hai.html\/#Nhung_gi_can_bao_gom_trong_mot_CV\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n bao g\u1ed3m trong m\u1ed9t CV:\">Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n bao g\u1ed3m trong m\u1ed9t CV:<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cv-so-voi-so-yeu-ly-lich-su-khac-biet-chinh-de-lua-chon-giua-hai.html\/#So_yeu_ly_lich\" title=\"S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch\">S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cv-so-voi-so-yeu-ly-lich-su-khac-biet-chinh-de-lua-chon-giua-hai.html\/#Nhung_gi_can_bao_gom_trong_mot_so_yeu_ly_lich\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n bao g\u1ed3m trong m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch:\">Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n bao g\u1ed3m trong m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch:<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cv-so-voi-so-yeu-ly-lich-su-khac-biet-chinh-de-lua-chon-giua-hai.html\/#Su_khac_biet-2\" title=\"S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t\">S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>CV l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0N\u00f3 c\u00f3 kh\u00e1c g\u00ec so v\u1edbi s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch kh\u00f4ng?<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea1i sao m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1ed9p h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 b\u1eb1ng CV so v\u1edbi s\u01a1 y\u1ebf l\u00fd l\u1ecbch s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch? C\u00f3 c\u00e1i n\u00e0o trong hai c\u00e1i n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 <em>t\u1ed1t<\/em>\u00a0h\u01a1n c\u00e1i kia kh\u00f4ng?\u00a0S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eeb kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a CV, v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i?<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Su_khac_biet\"><\/span><strong>S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u d\u00e0i t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ebfn hai trang tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh v\u1ec1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p, n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0CV (S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u d\u00e0i h\u01a1n tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y chi ti\u1ebft to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm vi\u1ec7c, CV \u2014 cho m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15082\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15082\" style=\"width: 1200px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15082 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/the_difference_between_a_cv_and_a_resume.jpg\" alt=\"CV-va-Resume\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1380\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/the_difference_between_a_cv_and_a_resume.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/the_difference_between_a_cv_and_a_resume-261x300.jpg 261w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/the_difference_between_a_cv_and_a_resume-890x1024.jpg 890w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/the_difference_between_a_cv_and_a_resume-768x883.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15082\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c nhau gi\u1eefa s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch v\u00e0 CV<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CV\"><\/span>CV<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>CV l\u00e0\u00a0g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><dfn>CV<\/dfn>\u00a0(m\u1eabu \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7\u00a0S\u01a1\u00a0<em>y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch<\/em>\u00a0, ti\u1ebfng Latinh c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \u201ccu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng\u201d) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chi ti\u1ebft.\u00a0N\u00f3 th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i hai ho\u1eb7c ba trang nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean 10 trang, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n.\u00a0S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch ch\u1ee9a th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c \u1ea5n ph\u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng, danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0\u1ede Hoa K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 Canada, CV ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp: c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, tr\u1ee3 c\u1ea5p, h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u, v.v.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"So_yeu_ly_lich_mau\"><\/span><strong>S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch m\u1eabu<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15083\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15083\" style=\"width: 2400px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15083 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cv_vs_resume_difference.jpg\" alt=\"So-yeu-ly-lich\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1280\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cv_vs_resume_difference.jpg 2400w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cv_vs_resume_difference-300x160.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cv_vs_resume_difference-1024x546.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cv_vs_resume_difference-768x410.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cv_vs_resume_difference-1536x819.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cv_vs_resume_difference-2048x1092.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2400px) 100vw, 2400px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15083\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y,\u00a0CV\u00a0r\u1ea5t chi ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n: nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea7n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea7u d\u00f2ng, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 v\u0103n b\u1ea3n (suy cho c\u00f9ng, \u00fd ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a CV l\u00e0\u00a0<em>m\u1ed9t\u00a0 l\u1ebd\u00a0<\/em><em>s\u1ed1ng<\/em>\u00a0, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u1ea1 khi n\u00f3 d\u00e0i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady!)<\/p>\n<p>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o CV.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhung_gi_can_bao_gom_trong_mot_CV\"><\/span><strong>Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n bao g\u1ed3m trong m\u1ed9t CV:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean l\u1ea1c<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u,\u00a0H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n\u00a0ho\u1eb7c Tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c<\/li>\n<li>C\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c h\u1eb9n h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/li>\n<li>S\u00e1ch<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e1ch<\/li>\n<li>\u1ea4n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ngang h\u00e0ng<\/li>\n<li>C\u00e1c \u1ea5n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00e1c<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 Danh hi\u1ec7u<\/li>\n<li>Tr\u1ee3 c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 H\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb<\/li>\n<li>Kinh nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y<\/li>\n<li>Kinh nghi\u1ec7m nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u \/ Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ph\u00f2ng th\u00ed nghi\u1ec7m \/ Nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u th\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ecba sau \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc<\/li>\n<li>Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng phi h\u1ecdc thu\u1eadt<\/li>\n<li>Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef v\u00e0 K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng<\/li>\n<li>Th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean<\/li>\n<li>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"So_yeu_ly_lich\"><\/span>S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch (hay\u00a0<dfn>r\u00e9sum\u00e9<\/dfn>\u00a0, t\u1eeb ti\u1ebfng Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u201ct\u00f3m l\u1ea1i\u201d) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn, s\u00fac t\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n xin vi\u1ec7c \u1edf M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 Canada.\u00a0M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch l\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p cho nh\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn t\u1ed5ng quan ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean.\u00a0M\u1ed9t s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch t\u1ed1t n\u00ean nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 d\u00e0i t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ebfn hai trang.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15084\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15084\" style=\"width: 2399px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15084 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/project_manager_resume_samples.jpg\" alt=\"So-yeu-ly-lich\" width=\"2399\" height=\"1279\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/project_manager_resume_samples.jpg 2399w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/project_manager_resume_samples-300x160.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/project_manager_resume_samples-1024x546.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/project_manager_resume_samples-768x409.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/project_manager_resume_samples-1536x819.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/project_manager_resume_samples-2048x1092.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2399px) 100vw, 2399px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15084\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhung_gi_can_bao_gom_trong_mot_so_yeu_ly_lich\"><\/span><strong>Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n bao g\u1ed3m trong m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7\u00a0bao g\u1ed3m\u00a0ch\u1ee9c danh c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c<\/li>\n<li>S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch\u00a0ho\u1eb7c\u00a0M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c<\/li>\n<li>Kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u0